Class 2

Runner Class:
will help us to execute our cucumber tests by Using JUnit

Hooks
are annotation based library which give us an opportunity to start a test and end the test
Hooks will be applied to all the test by default

@After annotation will be executed no matter of the test result.
Even if your test fails in the middle of the execution your @After hook will get executed

